{"tid":1288756,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"破牆者的吶喊 立會抗爭者心聲","createTime":"2019-07-05T18:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T18:27:04.000Z","uid":129225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a72735e93fb318b406cc5e94f00bc484a3439d37","tid":1288756,"uid":129225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:27:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190706/59792288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190706%2F59792288&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHbzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=bfd54970\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190706%2F59792288&h=d41bdf2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190706/59792288</a><br />\n<blockquote>作為首批衝擊者的C，在決定行動時已經知道需要承受的後果，「其實衝得入立會我都預咗係10碌8碌，最少係呢個數㗎啦，最簡單嘅刑事毀壞我哋都中咗㗎啦。」面對可能到來的牢獄生活，B引述了當晚身邊大多數人的想法，「如果香港同中國大陸一樣，都係俾共產黨帶領住嘅話，咁同坐監有乜嘢分別呢？」學生E的想法則更為純粹，「都係真係抱住必死心態，當我哋一諗起嗰三位走咗嘅義士，當下好似冇後顧之憂咁。」</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>「香港係我哋嘅屋企，我哋都唔去守護佢，冇人會守護佢㗎啦，我哋已經冇退路啦我哋，退無可退先會咁。我哋真係好鍾意呢個地方。」D如是說。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}